There are several forms of trading in our area.
Number 1:-{The filling station.} The filling station provides both the local community and the visiting tourists with petrol and also provides minor services.{(Section 2)}
Number 2:- {The campsite shop.} This shop provides the visiting tourists with some supplies, such as bread and milk, newspapers and postcards.{(Section 6)}
Number 3:- {Local newsagents.} Privideds locals as well as tourists with papers, sweets and small gifts. {(Section 2)}
